title: Intown Suites Premium room at 290 and 1960. Home Away From Home!
posting_body: ['WEELY RATE!!!', 'Welcome to the comfort of home.', 'Our new comfort rooms couldn’t have a more appropriate name.', 'Custom mattresses and seriously legit bedding.', 'We’ve also added premium TV channels, so much more storage, and a fully-furnished situation that looks like a million bucks.', 'Stay, play and even nap the day away.', '(We won’t tell.)', 'All this and so much more, at a zero-stress price.', 'More Storage', '-Built-in closets with organizers, too', '-Bathroom vanities and shelving with 2 mirrors, for looking twice as good', '-Wall hooks, aka most underrated invention ever', 'Added Comfort', '-Crazy amazing custom mattresses with fluffier bedding', '-Kitchen table for 2, for weekend catch-ups or weekday breakfast', 'Better Living', '-Fully furnished by someone who knows what they’re doing', '-FREE local & long distance calls and voicemail services', 'BOOK TODAY!!!', 'show contact info']
